  <notes notes-type="author-contribution">
    <title>Authors’ contributions</title>
    <p>T.M. performed the computational analysis, wrote the source code for CimpleG and the initial draft of the manuscript. M.S. compiled and curated the methylation data sets, provided suggestions and insight for the development of CimpleG and pre-processing of the datasets. M.S. and M.E. helped debugging and improving initial versions of the software. M.E. and I.C. annotated the CpG signatures. I.C. and W.W. designed and supervised the study. T.M., M.S., I.C. and W.W. conceptualized the project. All authors revised the manuscript and approved the final version.</p>
  </notes>
